---
title: Baja Salmon with Yellow Rice
description: Salsa fresca brings our favourite warm weather vibes. It’s juicy and tangy, with a touch of heat, making it the perfect complement to crispy, Mexican-spiced salmon. The feisty fillets are served on top of steamy yellow rice and finished with lime crema and salsa. Hello summer fresh!
